你能够调用以下的API:
[['FinancialInstitution.get_anti_unfair_competition_policy', {'name': 'FinancialInstitution.get_anti_unfair_competition_policy', 'description': 'Retrieve the anti-unfair competition policy of a specified financial institution.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'institution_name', 'description': 'The name of the financial institution.', 'type': 'STRING'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'policy_content', 'description': 'The content of the anti-unfair competition policy.'}]}], ['FinancialInstitution.analyze_policy_effectiveness', {'name': 'FinancialInstitution.analyze_policy_effectiveness', 'description': 'Analyze the effectiveness of the anti-unfair competition policy.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'policy_content', 'description': 'The content of the policy to be analyzed.', 'type': 'STRING'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'effectiveness_analysis', 'description': 'The analysis of the policy effectiveness.'}]}], ['FinancialInstitution.query_violation_records', {'name': 'FinancialInstitution.query_violation_records', 'description': 'Query the violation records of anti-unfair competition for a specified financial institution within a given time period.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'institution_name', 'description': 'The name of the financial institution.', 'type': 'STRING'}, {'name': 'time_period', 'description': 'The time period for which to query the records.', 'type': 'STRING'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'violation_records', 'description': 'The list of violation records.'}]}], ['FinancialInstitution.evaluate_management_level', {'name': 'FinancialInstitution.evaluate_management_level', 'description': 'Evaluate the management level of anti-unfair competition based on policy effectiveness and violation records.', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'policy_effectiveness', 'description': 'The effectiveness of the policy.', 'type': 'STRING'}, {'name': 'violation_records', 'description': 'The list of violation records.', 'type': 'STRING'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'management_level_evaluation', 'description': 'The evaluation of the management level.'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。
